OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1784130494
OL,3,CMan charged after tractor crashed into
OL,4,Chouse in Middlesbrough
OL,6,FA man has been charged in connection
OL,7,Fwith an incident where a tractor
OL,8,Fcrashed into a house.
OL,10,FEmergency services were called to
OL,11,FPriory Road in Middlesbrough at around
OL,12,F1am on Saturday 9 May after receiving
OL,13,Freports that a tractor had allegedly
OL,14,Fbeen used to damage a property.
OL,16,FCleveland Police have now confirmed
OL,17,Fthey have charged a 28-year-old man in
OL,18,Fconnection with the incident.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/2
