OL,3,CMan charged after tractor crashed into
OL,4,Chouse in Middlesbrough
OL,6,FHe has been charged with criminal
OL,7,Fdamage with intent to endanger life
OL,8,Fand aggravated vehicle taking and is
OL,9,Fdue to appear at Teesside Magistrates'
OL,10,FCourt on Wednesday 8 July.
